t\\/opera-studio-de-l-opera-national-du-rhin-a-colmar-3965_L\\">l\\u2019<strong>Op\\u00e9ra Studio<\\/strong>, cellule de formation pour jeunes chanteurs, \\u00e0 Colmar<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>La salle de Strasbourg, \\u00e0 configuration \\u00e0 l''italienne dispose de 1142 places.<\\/p><p>Apr\\u00e8s plus de trente ann\\u00e9es d''existence, l''exp\\u00e9rience alsacienne est devenue un mod\\u00e8le. Tout en demeurant farouchement attach\\u00e9 \\u00e0 ses racines r\\u00e9gionales et europ\\u00e9ennes,\\u00a0<strong>l''Op\\u00e9ra national du Rhin<\\/strong>\\u00a0s''est impos\\u00e9 comme une institution incontournable de la vie lyrique fran\\u00e7aise et internationale, r\\u00e9compens\\u00e9e en novembre 1997 par l\\u2019obtention du label \\u00abOp\\u00e9ra national\\u00bb. Il est dirig\\u00e9 depuis 2009 par Marc Cl\\u00e9meur, qui succ\\u00e8de \\u00e0 Nicholas Snowman.<\\/p><p><img class=\\"size-medium wp-image-159 aligncenter\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/opera-national-du-rhin-strasbourg-7097-685-0-300x200.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"300\\" height=\\"200\\" \\/><\\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"8af37e0","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"8e6554c","elType":"widget","settings":{"address":"Op\\u00e9ra national du Rhin - OnR 19 place Broglie 67000  Strasbourg  ","zoom":{"unit":"px","size":16}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"google_maps"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"98d26e1","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"71582f0","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"b3c1e85","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":33}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"61e4f67","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22"},"elements":[{"id":"b120ede","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null},"elements":