ra Studio<\\/strong>, cellule de formation pour jeunes chanteurs, \\u00e0 Colmar<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>La salle de Strasbourg, \\u00e0 configuration \\u00e0 l''italienne dispose de 1142 places.<\\/p><p>Apr\\u00e8s plus de trente ann\\u00e9es d''existence, l''exp\\u00e9rience alsacienne est devenue un mod\\u00e8le. Tout en demeurant farouchement attach\\u00e9 \\u00e0 ses racines r\\u00e9gionales et europ\\u00e9ennes,\\u00a0<strong>l''Op\\u00e9ra national du Rhin<\\/strong>\\u00a0s''est impos\\u00e9 comme une institution incontournable de la vie lyrique fran\\u00e7aise et internationale, r\\u00e9compens\\u00e9e en novembre 1997 par l\\u2019obtention du label \\u00abOp\\u00e9ra national\\u00bb. Il est dirig\\u00e9 depuis 2009 par Marc Cl\\u00e9meur, qui succ\\u00e8de \\u00e0 Nicholas Snowman.<\\/p><p><img class=\\"size-medium wp-image-159 aligncenter\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/opera-national-du-rhin-strasbourg-7097-685-0-300x200.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"300\\" height=\\"200\\" \\/><\\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"8af37e0","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"8e6554c","elType":"widget","settings":{"address":"Op\\u00e9ra national du Rhin - OnR 19 place Broglie 67000  Strasbourg  ","zoom":{"unit":"px","size":16}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"google_maps"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"98d26e1","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"71582f0","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"b3c1e85","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":33}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"61e4f67","elType":"section","settings":{"structure":"22"},"elements":[{"id":"b120ede","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":66,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"2abe97c","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h3 class=\\"intro\\">Cr\\u00e9\\u00e9 en 1928, le club strasbourgeois de la SIG \\u00e9volue au plus haut niveau dans le championnat national de Basket-Ball.<\\/h3><p>Les matchs \\u00e0 domicile se d\\u00e9roulent g\\u00e9n\\u00e9ralemet au\\u00a0<a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.jds.fr\\/strasbourg\\/grande-scene\\/hall-rhenus-strasbourg-420_L\\">Rh\\u00e9nus Sport<\\/a>\\u00a0\\u00e0 c\\u00f4t\\u00e9 du\\u00a0<a href=\\"https:\\/\\/www.jds.fr\\/strasbourg\\/parc-expo-alsace\\/parc-des-expositions-du-wacken-4589_L\\">parc de Expositions de Strasbourg<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>Retrouvez ci-dessous le calendrier complet de la\\u00a0<strong>saison de Pro A 2017-2018<\\/strong>, ainsi que les matchs de Basketball Champions League qui se d\\u00e9roulent au Hall Rh\\u00e9nus avec la\\u00a0<strong>SIG Basket-Ball Strasbourg<\\/strong>.<\\/p><p><img class=\\"size-medium wp-image-161 aligncenter\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/sig-basket-ball-strasbourg-70915-600-600-F-300x300.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"300\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false},{"id":"cba42ee","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":33,"_inline_size":null},"elements":[{"id":"1e6709e","elType":"widget","settings":{"address":"SIG Basket-Ball Strasbourg 17 boulevard de Dresde 67000  Strasbourg  ","zoom":{"unit":"px","size":14}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"google_maps"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]'),
